538
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:17,880
Mother, you and I are different.

539
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:21,360
I rather spend my life with my loved one.

540
00:33:21,560 --> 00:33:23,720
I am not as ambitious as Mother.

541
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:26,560
I cannot give up my love in exchange of power.

542
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:29,120
Please forgive me that I can't obey this order.

543
00:33:29,320 --> 00:33:31,040
Do you know what you're saying?

544
00:33:31,360 --> 00:33:32,600
I'm your Mother.

545
00:33:32,840 --> 00:33:34,639
Mother, would you rather see me as an Emperor...

546
00:33:35,080 --> 00:33:37,000
than a person with happiness?

547
00:33:37,639 --> 00:33:39,560
What you told me today...

548
00:33:39,639 --> 00:33:41,560
I will forget it,

549
00:33:41,800 --> 00:33:44,000
and will not say a single word to anyone.

550
00:33:44,280 --> 00:33:45,639
Mother, please forget today's conversation as well.

551
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:47,280
I need to deal with some military affairs.

552
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:48,760
I will take a leave now.

553
00:33:49,760 --> 00:33:52,239
You have to keep every single word in mind.

554
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:55,800
One day, you will understand why I said these.

555
00:33:56,040 --> 00:33:59,600
The world is not as easy as you think.

556
00:33:59,800 --> 00:34:02,679
I don't know when you will be clear-headed.

557
00:34:02,880 --> 00:34:04,719
But now,

558
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:07,080
getting married to Sui He is your only option!

559
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:19,639
Sui He.

560
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:22,360
Don't blame on Xu Feng.

561
00:34:25,720 --> 00:34:28,240
His Highness will understand you one day.

562
00:34:30,600 --> 00:34:32,800
Why will I blame on him?

563
00:34:34,640 --> 00:34:36,160
If I need to blame on someone,

564
00:34:36,680 --> 00:34:38,960
that person will be Jin Mi.

565
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:41,600
She bewitched His Highness's heart.

566
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:46,280
I'm surprised that Jin Mi is your daughter.

567
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:47,560
I'm surprised...

568
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,120
Your Majesty once thought that

569
00:34:49,400 --> 00:34:51,480
Jin Mi is the daughter of you and Zi Fen.

570
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:52,400
Luo Lin.

571
00:34:53,400 --> 00:34:54,880
What have you discovered?

572
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:57,680
I have discovered everything I need to know.

573
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:58,360
Luo Lin.

574
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:03,560
Zi Fen was my true love.

575
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:07,480
You said Zi Fen was your true love...

576
00:35:08,200 --> 00:35:10,440
Then why would you hurt her body...

577
00:35:10,720 --> 00:35:12,080
and break her heart?

578
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,920
I know.

579
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:16,000
It's all my fault.

580
00:35:16,400 --> 00:35:18,560
I was being jealous and stunned.

581
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:20,440
I arranged the marriage of you and Lin Xiu...

582
00:35:20,640 --> 00:35:22,200
was to keep Zi Fen by my side.

583
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,640
But I never knew...

584
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,840
she still left with regrets.

585
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:32,240
Do you know the reason behind Zi Fen's death?

586
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:34,960
According to Floral Realm's announcement,

587
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:37,600
after Zi Fen went back,

588
00:35:38,720 --> 00:35:40,280
she was unhappy all day long,

589
00:35:41,080 --> 00:35:45,040
and at the end... died with a grievance.

590
00:35:45,560 --> 00:35:46,880
Zi Fen.

591
00:35:47,120 --> 00:35:49,520
Do you really not want me to tell him?

592
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:54,480
You know Floral Realm and I are willing to die for you.

593
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:02,680
I'm willing to bear all the charges.

594
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:03,960
Bear?

595
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:06,440
Zi Fen is dead.

596
00:36:07,120 --> 00:36:08,840
My daughter,

597
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:11,320
in these 4000 years,

598
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:14,240
never saw her mother once!

599
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:16,560
How would you possible to bear it?

600
00:36:19,520 --> 00:36:20,440
I understand.

601
00:36:21,960 --> 00:36:23,600
In these 4000 years,

602
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:27,120
every time I think of this,

603
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:31,780
I cannot forgive myself.

604
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,560
Luo Lin.

605
00:36:36,920 --> 00:36:38,280
I'm now...

606
00:36:39,240 --> 00:36:41,680
I'm now begging you, as a friend,

607
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:45,760
I hope you and Zi Fen can forgive me.

608
00:36:47,240 --> 00:36:48,720
I have lost Zi Fen...

609
00:36:51,240 --> 00:36:53,360
I can't bear to lost my best friend as well.

610
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:59,280
I will not forgive you.

611
00:37:01,080 --> 00:37:02,320
Otherwise,

612
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:06,680
I can't face Zi Fen.

613
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:10,000
What I can do now

614
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:12,440
is too follow Zi Fen's will.

615
00:37:12,920 --> 00:37:15,640
An eye for an eye makes the whole world go blind.

616
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:20,840
To make the world stay peaceful,

617
00:37:22,520 --> 00:37:26,760
Zi Fen... would be the only one to be sacrificed.

618
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:28,680
I know.

619
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:32,960
Jin Mi is the daughter of you and Zi Fen.

620
00:37:33,640 --> 00:37:35,360
When she gets married to Run Yu,

621
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:39,600
she will be my daughter-in-law.

622
00:37:40,120 --> 00:37:41,040
By then,

623
00:37:42,360 --> 00:37:43,960
I will host...

624
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:46,680
the biggest wedding ceremony for them.

625
00:37:47,160 --> 00:37:48,440
As a...

626
00:37:49,400 --> 00:37:53,320
a little payback to you and Zi Fen.

627
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:59,240
If Jin Mi is not fond of Run Yu,

628
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:05,680
I will never allow my daughter to have any connection...

629
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:09,680
to Heaven Realm.

630
00:38:12,840 --> 00:38:15,160
You are so respected in Heaven Realm.

631
00:38:15,560 --> 00:38:18,120
I can't allow you to have any resentment to me.

632
00:38:19,480 --> 00:38:20,680
But, to Jin Mi,

633
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:23,240
I will treat her well sincerely.

